'''
Context instructions
====================

The context instructions represent non graphics elements like:

* Matrix manipulation (PushMatrix, PopMatrix, Rotate, Translate, Scale,
  MatrixInstruction)
* Color manipulation (Color)
* Texture binding (BindTexture)

